{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"I was thinking about my place in the universe,"},{"time":5000,"text":"and about my first thought about what infinity might mean,"},{"time":12000,"text":"when I was a child."},{"time":15000,"text":"And I thought that if time could reach"},{"time":19000,"text":"forwards and backwards infinitely,"},{"time":21000,"text":"doesn't that mean that"},{"time":23000,"text":"every point in time is really infinitely small,"},{"time":26000,"text":"and therefore somewhat meaningless."},{"time":28000,"text":"So we don't really have a place in the universe,"},{"time":30000,"text":"as far as on a time line."},{"time":32000,"text":"But nothing else does either."},{"time":34000,"text":"Therefore every moment really is the most important moment"},{"time":37000,"text":"that's ever happened, including this moment right now."},{"time":40000,"text":"And so therefore this music you're about to hear"},{"time":42000,"text":"is maybe the most important music"},{"time":44000,"text":"you'll ever hear in your life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":238000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":241000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":243000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":524000,"text":"For those of you who I'll be fortunate enough to meet afterwards,"},{"time":528000,"text":"you could please refrain from saying,"},{"time":530000,"text":"\"Oh my god, you're so much shorter in real life.\""},{"time":534000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":537000,"text":"Because it's like the stage is an optical illusion,"},{"time":540000,"text":"for some reason."},{"time":542000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":546000,"text":"Somewhat like the curving of the universe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":548000,"text":"I don't know what it is. I get asked in interviews a lot,"},{"time":551000,"text":"\"My god, you're guitars are so gigantic!\""},{"time":554000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":555000,"text":"\"You must get them custom made -- special, humongous guitars.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":558000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":849000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":852000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":854000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}